section.featuresSlider
  .featuresSlider__content
    h2.subPage__title.featuresSlider__title Key Features
    .featuresSlider__btns
      button.featuresSlider-btn.featuresSlider-btn_left
        | left
        +icon('arrow')
      button.featuresSlider-btn.featuresSlider-btn_right
        | Right
        +icon('arrow')
  .swiper.featuresSlider-swiper
    ul.featuresSlider-list.swiper-wrapper
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Seamless Integration
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Embed via SDK, white-label widgets, or branded dApps. Fully compatible with custody solutions and ERC-7540 / ERC-4626 standards.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Automated Risk Management
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Real-time monitoring with automated triggers for liquidation protection, diversification, and dynamic allocation based on APY and security.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Whitelabel Yield Widgets
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Plug-and-play yield components with full branding options and enterprise dashboard controls.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Asset Diversification
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Deploy user assets into diversified vault baskets without giving up custody. Diversification actions are driven by programmable triggers and risk thresholds – for example, automatically balancing exposures when volatility rises – to maintain a healthy, compliant asset mix at all times.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Pre-Pooling Operations
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Execute essential steps before funds enter the vault to mitigate risk. For instance, Ditto can perform token swaps or stablecoin distribution in advance, so that assets are in the optimal form for your strategy.
